<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Automated Annual Report Preparation Portal for Educational Institutes</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset and styling for the page */
        body, h1, h2, h3, p {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        /* Header styles */
        header {
            background-color: #004080;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
        }

        header .logo {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .auth-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .auth-buttons a {
            color: #004080;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .auth-buttons a:hover {
            background-color: #cce0ff;
        }

        /* Main content styles */
        .banner {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 400px;
            background-image: url('path-to-your-image.jpg'); /* Replace with an actual image path */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .banner h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #004080;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .content p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        /* Footer styles */
        footer {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }

        footer p {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <header>
        <div class="logo">Educational Report Portal</div>
        <nav>
            <a href="#">Home</a>
            <a href="#">About</a>
            <a href="#">Contact Us</a>
        </nav>
        <div class="auth-buttons">
            <a href="#">Sign Up</a>
            <a href="#">Sign In</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Banner Section -->
    <section class="banner">
        <div>
            <h1>Automated Annual Report Preparation Portal</h1>
            <p>Streamlining report generation for educational institutes with data integration, analysis, and visualization.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content Section -->
    <main class="content">
        <h2>About the Platform</h2>
        <p>Our Automated Annual Report Preparation Portal is designed to simplify the process of compiling, analyzing, and presenting data for educational institutes. By automating data collection and integration from multiple sources, we enable institutes to generate insightful, comprehensive annual reports effortlessly.</p>

        <h2>Key Features</h2>
        <p>This platform offers secure role-based access, customizable dashboards for analyzing data, and multimedia-rich report generation capabilities. Collaborative tools and compliance with educational standards ensure accuracy and efficiency, empowering institutions to reduce manual effort and enhance data-driven insights.</p>

        <h2>Why Choose Our Platform?</h2>
        <p>Our user-friendly interface, combined with advanced data visualization, makes it easier for institutes to track progress and performance over the year. The system supports multi-user collaboration, ensuring that the entire institution can contribute to creating a report that reflects every aspect of its achievements and challenges.</p>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer Section -->
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Educational Report Portal. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>Designed to enhance data-driven reporting for educational excellence.</p>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>